		<h2 class="comic-title">Invincible</h2>
		<p>Invincible is a fun superhero book where the main protagonist is the son of a super powered alien and discovers he has powers of his own. Invincible's dad is on earth and is it's current mightiest hero.</p>

		<p><b>OMG Moment:</b> Invincible's father reveals that he has been sent to earth to prepare it for the eventual arrival of all his super powered buddies to enslave the humans and breed with their women. Invincible doesn't like that so his father nearly kills him, but right before administering the killing blow, he flies off into outer space.</p>